textAfterTable: Profile Aberdeen Global - Emerging Markets Infrastructure Equity Fund is an open-end fund incorporated in Luxembourg. The Fund's objective is long-term total return. The Fund invests at least two-thirds of its assets in equities and equity-related securities of companies active in infrastructure-related sectors, which have their registered office in an emerging-market country.
